data.description: A two-story traditional home with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The one-car garage provides a convenient space for parking and storage, while the large, fenced-in yard is great for outdoor activities, gardening, or for those with pets.    This homes offer a classic and timeless architectural style that appeals to many homebuyers. The number of bedrooms and bathrooms suit the needs of a starting family or couple, and the fence in the yard can provide privacy and security.
